---
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro";
import UMLogo from "./UMLogo.astro";
---

<section id="contact" class="bg-black py-12 md:py-20 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- タイトル -->
    <SectionTitle title="お問い合わせ" />
    <div class="text-white text-center mb-8 md:mb-12 px-2 md:px-20">
      <div
        class="bg-green-900 rounded-xl px-6 py-6 md:px-8 md:py-8 shadow-xl h-full flex items-center justify-center"
      >
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-green-100 text-sm md:text-base font-medium mb-4">
            無料体験についてのお問い合わせは<br />お電話ください。
          </p>
          <a
            href="tel:070-9000-8811"
            class="inline-block bg-green-700 hover:bg-green-800 text-white text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-wider px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105"
          >
            070-9000-8811
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="my-8">
          無料体験以外のお問い合わせは
          <a class="text-lime-200" href="https://umgolf68.com/contact/"
            >こちら</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
